Package: hsiaotest
Title: Hsiao Tests for Panel Homogeneity
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Boussiala", "Mohamed Nachid", email = "boussiala.nachid@univ-alger3.dz", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides standard and robust implementations of Hsiao's tests 
    for homogeneity of intercepts and slopes in panel data. Includes F-tests 
    and heteroskedasticity-consistent versions using sandwich estimators.
